pages.name: Privacy Policy
pages.description:
• Information Collection

    • We do not collect, store, or process any personal information from users.
    • When you visit our website, you can browse and use our services without providing any personal details.

  • Third-Party Services

    • Our website may display links to third-party websites or services (e.g., online stores offering discounts). Please note that these platforms operate independently, and we recommend reviewing their privacy policies before engaging with them.

  • Your Privacy Rights

    • Since we do not collect user information, there is no personal data to manage, update, or delete.

  • Commitment to Privacy

    • We ensure that your browsing experience on Try The Deal is secure and free from any personal data handling.

pages.name: Cookies Policy
pages.description:
• What Are Cookies?
    Cookies are small files stored on your device that help websites function efficiently and enhance user experience.

  • Our Use of Cookies

    • We do not use cookies to collect or store any personally identifiable information.
    • Cookies may be used to improve website performance, such as loading speed and user interface.
    • Any cookies used are anonymous and cannot be traced back to you.

  • Managing Cookies

    • You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. However, this may impact the functionality of certain website features.

  • Third-Party Cookies

    • Our site may feature third-party content, such as affiliate links to stores or promotional codes. These third parties may use their own cookies, and we encourage you to review their cookie policies.
